High Level Goals:
  1. Enhance crop yield prediction - provide others with tools that help predict crop yields more accurately
  2. Inform climate agriculture practices - To help farmers researchers, etc to understand how climate change might impact crop production and come up with strategies for adaption
  3. Support data/decision making - To have user with accessible data to make informed decisions about planting, allocation, and risk management
  4. Promote sustainable agriculture - To have more efforts going into more sustainable agriculture practices by showing the enviornmental impacts of differet approaches and climate conditions
    
